  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/3391",
  "title": "IE11 doesn't work  anymore",
  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nIt seems that InstantSearch doesn't work anymore with IE 11.\r\nI try to use polyfill (like on the doc) but it doesn't work...\r\n\r\nIt work well before i change the rooting config. Previously i was using urlsync. \r\n\r\nI have a console error `\":\" expected` on the line of the stateToRoute function.\r\n\r\nPolyfill never works when i was using urlsync. So i had to block the website for IE < 11.\r\n\r\nNow it seems that i have to block it for all IE, that i don't want.\r\n\r\nThanks for your help.\r\n\r\nI use :\r\nhttps://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js\r\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/algoliasearch/3/algoliasearch.min.js\r\nhttps://cdn.polyfill.io/v2/polyfill.min.js?features=default,Array.prototype.includes\r\n",
